<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Resolve Voting Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #000000;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    
    .email-container {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 10px auto;
      border: 1px solid #cccccc;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    
    .header {
      height: 87px;
      background-color: #002347;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    
    .header-content {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    
    .logo {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    
    .logo img {
      height: 26px;
      width: auto;
    }
    
    .website-link {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    
    .banner {
      background-color: #EEEDF8;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      height: 86px;
    }
    
    .banner-content {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    .banner-text {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    
    .banner-image {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .banner-image img {
      height: 60px;
      width: auto;
    }
    
    .banner-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 236px;
    }
    
    .banner-subtitle {
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #1F2124;
      width: 225px;
    }
    
    .main-content {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    
    .invitation-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 20px 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .body-text {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #1F2124;
      padding: 8px 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .details-section {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    
    .details-title {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #1F2124;
      margin: 0 0 5px;
    }
    
    .detail-item {
      font-size: 10px;
      margin: 0 0 5px;
    }
    
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .voting-link {
      color: #7FB4F1;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .message-section {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .signature {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #1F2124;
    }
    
    .signature span {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    
    .footer {
      background-color: #002347;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
      height: 161px;
    }
    
    .footer-top {
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .footer-logo {
      float: left;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .footer-logo img {
      height: 13px;
      width: auto;
    }
    
    .footer-tagline {
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    
    .social-icons {
      float: right;
    }
    
    .social-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #808080;
      border-radius: 50%;
      padding: 4px;
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      margin-left: 5px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .social-icon img {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
    }
    
    .footer-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.1);
      margin: 10px 0;
      clear: both;
    }
    
    .footer-bottom {
      overflow: hidden;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
    
    .footer-message {
      float: left;
      width: 164px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    
    .footer-copyright {
      float: right;
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #999999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dueipgl4k/image/upload/v1741814245/Frame_2147227052_cyssv9.png" alt="Resolve Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="website-link">
          https://resolve.vote/
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-content">
        <div class="banner-text">
          <h2 class="banner-title">Resolve it all—easy elections, trusted results</h2>
          <p class="banner-subtitle">If you have any questions or need assistance, contact our support team at info.resolvevote@gmail.com.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="banner-image">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dueipgl4k/image/upload/v1741814246/FY25-Voter_Registration-frames-3-1000x1000_rgkk6c.png" alt="Vote Icon">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="main-content">
      <h2 class="invitation-title">You've Been Invited to Vote! An Election Has Just Been Created.</h2>
      <p class="greeting">Hi {{voterName}},</p>
      <p class="body-text">An election has just been created, and your vote matters!</p>
      
      <div class="details-section">
        <p class="details-title">Here are the details:</p>
        <p class="detail-item"><span class="detail-label">Election Name:</span> {{electionTitle}}</p>
        <p class="detail-item"><span class="detail-label">Voting Period:</span> {{electionStartDate}} - {{electionEndDate}}</p>
        <p class="detail-item"><span class="detail-label">Voting Link:</span> <a href="{{electionLink}}" class="voting-link">{{electionLink}}</a></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="message-section">
        <p class="body-text">Your vote is safe, secure, and only takes a few seconds! Click the unique link to participate:</p>
        <p class="body-text">See you at the polls!</p>
        <p class="signature">
          <span>Best regards,</span>
          The Resolve Team
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-logo">
          <img src="https://example.com/resolve-logo.png" alt="Resolve Logo">
          <div class="footer-tagline">
            Secure Elections, <br> Trusted Results
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <div class="social-icon">
            <img src="https://example.com/instagram-icon.png" alt="Instagram">
          </div>
          <div class="social-icon">
            <img src="https://example.com/facebook-icon.png" alt="Facebook">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer-divider"></div>
      
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <div class="footer-message">
          Start with Resolve: Create, manage, and monitor your elections effortlessly.
        </div>
        <div class="footer-copyright">
          © Resolve Rights Reserved 2024
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>